    "body" : "<p>The inverse of XOR is XOR itself. <br>\nI came across a similar problem on leetcode. <a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/decode-xored-array/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Leetcode-1720</a> <br></p>\n"
