  "title" : "What is the inverse function to XOR?",
  "body" : "<p>There is XOR function in Java - <code>a^b</code></p>\n<p>For example: <code>5^3 = 6</code></p>\n<p>Can you tell me the inverse function? If I have <code>6</code> and <code>3</code> can I get range of numbers which include number <code>5</code>?</p>\n"
